
ConnorA boy faking a smile on a daily basis, depressed. Hiding his depression. When he meets Skye, his life takes a spin.
SkyeA Girl faking her smile on a daily basis. Just like Connor is hiding her depression. Will her and Connors broken pieces stick back together or will it continue to fall apart.
LauraSkye's best friend, knows she's sad, but doesn't understand, but she will soon...